      "title": "3215 arrested for May 9 incident",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Police Media Spokesman Senior Superintendent of Police Advocate Mr. Nihal Talduwa says that 3215 suspects have been arrested so far in relation to the reported incidents related to the violent and riotous acts that took place across the island on the day of May.",
        "The media spokesman added that 1176 of those suspects have been remanded in custody."
      ],
